The paper discusses concerns and limitations of deep learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also mentions progress in areas such as image recognition (cs.CV) and speech recognition (cs.CL), which are applications of deep learning. The paper also mentions the need for supplementing deep learning with other techniques, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
